The Foreign Affairs Ministry is on the spot for acquiring a property in Kampala for Sh650 million instead of Sh250 million. Principal Secretary Macharia Kamau was hard-pressed to explain why the ministry decided to drop the lowest bidder in favour of the highest one. ALSO READ:

